{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":80,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-14T23:41:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222850547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479149365\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSituation hasn\u0027t occurred, I\u0027m sure something could be worked out one way or another.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK, thanks for the reply!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T07:49:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many warning points did you guys get before you became moderators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T12:44:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222852566\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479282595\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many warning points did you guys get before you became moderators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s a less simple question than it appears, as the scale has changed with the move to IPS. Warnings are usually 0-5 points now, with 5 resulting in queuing. Under vB they were typically 5-25pts, with 25 being a queuing and 0-point warnings being handled differently.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think I may be the mod with the worst warning/infraction history, I had three warnings and one\u00A0serious infraction before becoming a mod. The other mods had at most a warning or two, with most having clean records.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T13:28:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough I do not think I have ever had a post removed by a mod (as far as I can recall), if a moderator does remove a post, does the user\u0027s post count go down by the number of posts removed? I\u0027ve noticed an increase in posts being removed in the last few weeks and wondered what happens...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T14:12:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222852780\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479302903\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough I do not think I have ever had a post removed by a mod (as far as I can recall), if a moderator does remove a post, does the user\u0027s post count go down by the number of posts removed? I\u0027ve noticed an increase in posts being removed in the last few weeks and wondered what happens...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt doesn\u0027t, removed posts still count.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit - by the way, posts in some sub forums (I believe The Lounge and its subs, tho I\u0027m not sure) don\u0027t count, removed or not. So, users who only hang around forum games may have their post count a lot lower than they expect.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-17T10:24:15Z\u0022 title=\u002211/17/2016 10:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by monstah\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"worir4","CreatedById":75980,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T18:53:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe forum just went off line for everyone, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T18:57:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222853108\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479322398\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002275980\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022worir4\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, worir4 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe forum just went off line for everyone, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome maintenance work led to an unexpected interruption in service.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNormality is now restored.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T19:04:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222853114\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479322668\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022131400\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starhawk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Starhawk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNormality is now restored.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, except \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0is now a bowl of petunias.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-16T19:06:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGive \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/95210-monstah/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002295210\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/95210-monstah/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@monstah\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 the keys to the kingdom and the whole forum crashes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-17T03:53:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222852566\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479282595\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many warning points did you guys get before you became moderators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had one warn, but it was from before points were a thing. KasperVld said I was being too snarky. Which I was. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Padishar","CreatedById":97386,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-17T17:12:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222853665\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479354783\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had one warn, but it was from before points were a thing. KasperVld said I was being too snarky. Which I was. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCareful, public discussion of moderator actions is against the rules and could get you another one... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-19T01:03:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222853123\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479323049\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002295210\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022monstah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/16/2016 at 11:04 AM, monstah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, except \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0is now a bowl of petunias.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs that a whale over there?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CAKE99","CreatedById":150099,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T08:08:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow are members selected to become moderators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd would it be possible to add the\u00A0date a moderator became a moderator on the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/74320-your-moderators/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eyour moderators\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0thread? (So it would display as \u0022[moderator role]: [moderator username] [moderator join date]\u0022)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T11:22:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222860252\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479802112\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150099\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CAKE99\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, CAKE99 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow are members selected to become moderators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my case, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002212858\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Red Iron Crown\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0threw a dart at a board, and it landed in my name \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJoking aside, I once expressed that, if they needed, I was available. Some things help: being around for awhile, being helpful, having time to dedicate to it, being fluent in another language (in my case, you can say I\u0027m fluent in\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ethis\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0language, since my own is Portuguese \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0) since there is an international section, having no infractions. None of these are required on their own, I think, but that sort of thing makes the stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving moderators in different time zones is good too, since we can mod at any time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T11:30:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222860252\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479802112\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150099\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CAKE99\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, CAKE99 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow are members selected to become moderators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOccasionally there has\u00A0been a public request for volunteers, but generally we add moderators by invitation. When it is determined that we need new mods, we start a thread in the moderators\u0027 area of the forum asking for nominations, then we discuss the pros and cons of each before sending out invites.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, CAKE99 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd would it be possible to add the\u00A0date a moderator became a moderator on the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/74320-your-moderators/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eyour moderators\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0thread? (So it would display as \u0022[moderator role]: [moderator username] [moderator join date]\u0022)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure all the dates are available, plus we wouldn\u0027t want people to be dismissive of a moderator because they\u0027ve only been doing it for a month or something.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222860382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479813724\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002295210\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022monstah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, monstah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving moderators in different time zones is good too, since we can mod at any time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Sun never sets on the Moderation Empire.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T11:32:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222860386\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479814216\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Sun never sets on the Moderation Empire.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Banana Is Always Watching\u2122\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-24T03:06:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022table-layout:fixed;width:789px;line-height:1.6;color:rgb(39,42,52);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-top:0px;font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(128,0,0);\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u0026lt;Merged in from seperate thread\u0026gt;\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\nI was wondering, when a moderator opens the forums and logs in, what does he see? I mean, it can\u0027t just be a normal interface- how else do they manage to edit comments, lock threads, etc? There gotta be something else, right? How does the whole system work from a moderator\u0027s perspective?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-24T06:57:50Z\u0022 title=\u002211/24/2016 06:57  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 24, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Val\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EMerged\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-24T04:11:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222862608\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479956800\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was wondering, when a moderator opens the forums and logs in, what does he see?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI imagine it\u0027s something like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ruins%20cityscapes%20fire%20artwork%20ap\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.knowledgehi.com/thumbnails/detail/20121022/ruins%20cityscapes%20fire%20artwork%20apocalyptic%201280x800%20wallpaper_www.knowledgehi.com_54.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-24T09:37:15Z\u0022 title=\u002211/24/2016 09:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 24, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by 5thHorseman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded a quote of the person I was talking to, back before the threads were merged.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-24T04:56:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#800000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u0026lt;Merged in from seperate thread\u0026gt;\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt was recently suggested to me that \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/62955-deddly/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002262955\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/62955-deddly/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Deddly\u003C/a\u003E listens to Christian rock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this true?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-24T06:55:15Z\u0022 title=\u002211/24/2016 06:55  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 24, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Val\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EMerged\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"diomedea","CreatedById":93700,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-24T11:09:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222862608\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479956800\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022table-layout:fixed;width:789px;line-height:1.6;color:rgb(39,42,52);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-top:0px;font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(128,0,0);\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u0026lt;Merged in from seperate thread\u0026gt;\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\nI was wondering, when a moderator opens the forums and logs in, what does he see? I mean, it can\u0027t just be a normal interface- how else do they manage to edit comments, lock threads, etc? There gotta be something else, right? How does the whole system work from a moderator\u0027s perspective?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInterface isn\u0027t much different from what normal users see. We have a few options with all normal users posts (where you find the quote button) and threads, can find some more info about users (mostly from their profile, something by simply mousing over their avatar) and with the same menu where account settings are, can access the moderator control panel, good to see all the reported things and queued posts nicely listed, plus a few other useful things. Plus, we have access to some hidden forum areas and can have notifications enabled about a number of \u0022events\u0022, e.g. when something gets reported. But there\u0027s nothing strikingly different in the way IPS software works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222862668\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479960695\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI imagine it\u0027s something like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ruins%20cityscapes%20fire%20artwork%20ap\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.knowledgehi.com/thumbnails/detail/20121022/ruins%20cityscapes%20fire%20artwork%20apocalyptic%201280x800%20wallpaper_www.knowledgehi.com_54.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly after some new KSP release....\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-24T11:48:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222862608\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479956800\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022table-layout:fixed;width:789px;line-height:1.6;color:rgb(39,42,52);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-top:0px;font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\nI was wondering, when a moderator opens the forums and logs in, what does he see?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nButtons, and warnings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike Dio said, not much changes, but there are a few extra clickables, and a new notification icon for mod stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe thing that I was most unsure about was this little button that appeared on top-right of posts and had no tooltip. I was so afraid I\u0027d click it and do something \u003Ci\u003Ebad\u003C/i\u003E, but it turned out it was just a checkbox for selecting posts (to move, remove, etc.) \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-24T12:28:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222862897\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479988088\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002295210\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022monstah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n39 minutes ago, monstah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nturned out it was just a checkbox for selecting posts\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPro moderators moderate in\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ebulk\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-25T02:33:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222862923\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479990498\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPro moderators moderate in\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ebulk\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBulk moderation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve never seen a contradiction in 5 words before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-25T03:34:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anyone been perma\u0027d from the forums before? Also, what is the worst punishment RIGHT BEFORE a ban?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-25T11:37:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222863684\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221480044891\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022138353\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HoloYolo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, HoloYolo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anyone been perma\u0027d from the forums before? Also, what is the worst punishment RIGHT BEFORE a ban?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA few people have, but probably fewer than you think (if you don\u0027t count spambots, if you do then it\u0027s probably more than you think).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe usual steps of escalating moderation measures goes something like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0-point warning -\u0026gt; Warning with points -\u0026gt; Placed in the moderation queue -\u0026gt; Temporary ban -\u0026gt; Permanent ban\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut that is very much subject to circumstances and severity of the matter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}